Class PendingDrawable

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.graphics.drawable.Drawable
      • com.atakmap.android.vehicle.model.icon.PendingDrawable
  • public class PendingDrawable
extends android.graphics.drawable.Drawable
    Bitmap-based drawable that may not be loaded on initial use

    Used for vehicle icons which are not immediately available if they have not been generated yet
